Microwave chocolate in medium microwaveable bowl on HIGH 2 min. or until almost melted, stirring after 1 min. Stir until chocolate is completely melted. Spread half of the chocolate on wax paper-covered baking sheet; sprinkle with crushed candies. Drizzle evenly with remaining chocolate. Refrigerate 1-1/2 hours or until firm. Break into 10 pieces. Store in tightly covered container at room temperature.